Interface IGenTDFactor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithmImpl, NetGenAdjustAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public interface IGenTDFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'IArea TD Factor'. Interface of generator shifting factor calculation methods for one or a set of injection buses and one or a set of withdraw buses.
    See Also:
    DclfAlgorithmPackage.getIGenTDFactor()
